71 (m) Nothing in this section shall be construed to impede the department of public health
72 or local health boards from investigating a reported foodborne illness.
73 (n) Nothing in this section shall preclude the department of public health or local health
74 boards from providing assistance, consultation, or an inspection at the request of the producer of
75 a cottage food product.
